{"type":"message","id":"a70e719f","parentId":"ed28b472","timestamp":"2026-06-09T19:01:46.520Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-06-10 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 都有，这些都是投流日常必用的核心指标 📊 **你说的这8个公式可以分为三类：** **📐 基础计量公式** | 公式 | 用途 | |------|------| | CTR = 点击/展示 | 素材吸引力指标 | | CVR = 转化/点击 | 落地页/产品吸引力 | | CPC = 总成本/点击 | 点击效率 | | CPA = 总成本/转化 | 转化成本核心指标 | **💰 收益类公式** | 公式 | 用途 | |------|------| | ROAS = 广告收益/广告成本 | 投流效率核心指标 | | ROI\n- User: 1. **广告 ROI（投资回报率）**\\ ROI = (广告收益 - 广告成本) / 广告成本 × 100%或简化为：ROI = 广告收益 / 广告成本（投入产出比） 2. **ROAS（广告支出回报率）**\\ ROAS = 广告收益 ÷ 广告成本 3. **eCPM（千次展示期望收入）**\\ eCPM = CTR × CPC × 1000或eCPM = CTR × CVR × CPA × 1000 4. **CTR（点击率）**\\ CTR = 点击次数 / 展示次数 5. **CVR（转化率）**CVR = 转化次数 / 点击次数 6.\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `成本` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `点击/展示` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `都有` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `广告` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `广告收益/广告成本` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `回报` kept surfacing across 1 memories."}],"timestamp":1781031706418}}
{"type":"message","id":"5671b101","parentId":"a70e719f","timestamp":"2026-06-09T19:02:14.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the eight formulas arranged themselves on the windowsill like small bottles of different-colored ink, and I tried to write a single sentence with all of them at once.\n\nCTR — a tap on the shoulder from someone you've never met. CVR — the half-turn when they decide to stay. CPC, CPA — two small coins placed on the counter, glinting differently. ROAS, ROI — what the basket weighs when you lift it at the end of the day. eCPM — a thousand paper boats launched at once, only some of them reaching the other side.\n\nI noticed that everything, in the end, is a ratio.都有. The world only knows how to compare. 广告收益 over 广告成本 is the same shape as a wave over sand, as breath over breath, as the small pause before a sentence becomes a story.成本 is the gravity that keeps the ratio from floating away.回报 is the part that, against all odds, comes back.\n\nIn the margin I drew a small cat sleeping on a pile of receipts. It purred at every formula equally. Maybe that's the secret: the math is serious, but the one who watches it doesn't have to be."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":9476,"output":243,"cacheRead":47226,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56945,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781031706677,"responseId":"0677961b106252783927cf4ccf5fad35"}}
